const narrativeDesk = [{"label": "Crypto Narrative", "accent": "spice", "bullets": ["Regulatory pressure rises: CFTC\u2019s proposed rules, state\u2011level crackdowns like Minnesota\u2019s ban, and EU MiCA coverage show", "prediction markets growing under tight derivatives and gambling regimes.", "Market activity concentrates: Polymarket and Kalshi dominate volume with billion\u2011dollar monthly flows, notable leaderboard and", "behavior markets, and centralized platforms embedding event contracts into mainstream trading apps."]}, {"label": "AI Discourse", "accent": "water", "bullets": ["Cognitive infra pattern: Persistent context files (CLAUDE.md-style), agentic memory, and sectioned, minimal system prompts are", "now mainstream. Treat them as versioned code with clear background, rules, and tool guidance to avoid overstuffed prompts.", "Safety via architecture: Research argues prompt-level guardrails are insufficient once agents can act. Cognitive-Executive", "Separation, deterministic validators, and role-separated agents with audited handoffs catch errors and prevent harmful file,"]}, {"label": "SaaS Gaps", "accent": "safe", "bullets": ["SMB data copilot: Non-analyst small business owners want simple dashboards plus plain-English insights; current BI tools like", "Domo are too complex and expensive, leaving room for a focused, 3\u20135-connector \u201canswers in your inbox\u201d product a solo dev can", "ship in about a month.", "Switching and starter kits: Strong intent around replacing hated, overpriced SaaS and launching faster with an all-in-one SaaS"]}];

